            <p class="- topic/p ">Install FFmpeg via Homebrew with <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph ">$ brew install ffmpeg</codeph>,</p>
            <p class="- topic/p ">OR</p>
          </li><li class="- topic/li ">Install it manually:</li><li class="- topic/li ">Go to the <xref format="html" href="https://ffmpeg.org/download.html" scope="external" class="- topic/xref ">FFmpeg
               download web page</xref>.</li><li class="- topic/li ">Download the package which is appropriate for your operating
